...that you lock yourself in to take them on one at a time?

27
00:03:52,365 --> 00:03:56,267
其实我一共有七个对手
Actually, there were seven of them.

28
00:03:56,437 --> 00:03:58,735
我只算到有六个 韦恩先生
l counted six, Mr. Wayne.

29
00:04:02,510 --> 00:04:03,738
你怎么知道我的名字?
How do you know my name?

30
00:04:03,911 --> 00:04:06,971
布鲁斯韦恩仍是个大人物
The world is too small for someone like Bruce Wayne to disappear...

31
00:04:07,148 --> 00:04:09,480
不管你有多么落魄潦倒
...no matter how deep he chooses to sink.

32
00:04:09,649 --> 00:04:10,775
你是谁?
Who are you?

33
00:04:10,952 --> 00:04:14,115
敝姓杜卡 我是忍者大师的代言人
My name is merely Ducard, but l speak for Ra's al Ghul...

34
00:04:14,288 --> 00:04:17,917
他是犯罪集团的克星
...a man greatly feared by the criminal underworld.

35
00:04:18,092 --> 00:04:19,684
