A man who can offer you a path.

36
00:04:20,595 --> 00:04:23,086
你凭什么认为我需要指引?
What makes you think l need a path?

37
00:04:23,497 --> 00:04:26,091
你这种人是自愿来这种地方
Someone like you is only here by choice.

38
00:04:26,267 --> 00:04:28,633
你想深入了解罪犯的世界
You have been exploring the criminal fraternity...

39
00:04:28,803 --> 00:04:31,271
不管你的目的是什么
...but whatever your original intentions...

40
00:04:32,006 --> 00:04:35,339
你已经迷失了方向
...you have become truly lost.

41
00:04:36,878 --> 00:04:40,644
