42
00:04:40,815 --> 00:04:44,808
你和他一样痛恨邪恶力量
The path of a man who shares his hatred of evil...

43
00:04:44,986 --> 00:04:48,217
你也希望能伸张正义
...and wishes to serve true justice.

44
00:04:48,688 --> 00:04:50,781
