...then you become something else entirely.

52
00:05:20,888 --> 00:05:22,412
什么人?
Which is?

53
00:05:22,924 --> 00:05:25,893
传奇英雄 韦恩先生
Legend, Mr. Wayne.

54
00:05:27,228 --> 00:05:28,820
明天你将被释放
Tomorrow, you will be released.

55
00:05:28,995 --> 00:05:32,396
如果你想打击更凶狠的罪犯
lf you are bored of brawling with thieves and want to achieve something...

56
00:05:32,566 --> 00:05:36,024
东边的山坡有一种罕见的蓝花
...there is a rare blue flower that grows on the eastern slopes.

57
00:05:36,203 --> 00:05:37,898
摘下一朵蓝花
Pick one of these flowers.

58
00:05:38,072 --> 00:05:41,041
如果你能把它带到山巅
lf you can carry it to the top of the mountain...

59
00:05:41,208 --> 00:05:44,006
也许就能找到你当初在寻找的东西
...you may find what you were looking for in the first place.

60
00:05:44,178 --> 00:05:47,011
我在寻找什么?
And what was l looking for?

61
00:05:48,749 --> 00:05:50,683
只有你自己知道
Only you can know that.

62
00:06:57,852 --> 00:07:01,447
回去 你一定要回头
You turn back. You go back.

63
00:08:09,423 --> 00:08:11,084
忍者大师?
Ra's al Ghul?

64
00:08:21,302 --> 00:08:22,860
且慢
