And make no mistake, here you face death.

77
00:09:29,270 --> 00:09:30,635
虎爪
Tiger.

78
00:09:32,239 --> 00:09:34,036
柔术
Jujitsu.

79
00:09:36,243 --> 00:09:37,301
豹掌
Panther.

80
00:09:40,814 --> 00:09:43,112
身手不错 但这不是儿戏
You're skilled. But this is not a dance.

81
00:09:48,589 --> 00:09:50,147
而且你仍然害怕
And you are afraid.

82
00:09:53,093 --> 00:09:54,958
但不是怕我
But not of me.

83
00:09:58,432 --> 00:10:00,923
告诉我 韦恩先生
Tell us, Mr. Wayne...

84
00:10:05,439 --> 00:10:08,602
你害怕什么?
...what do you fear?

85
00:10:17,751 --> 00:10:19,184
布鲁斯?
Bruce?

86
00:10:21,822 --> 00:10:24,313
没事了 没事了
lt's okay. lt's okay.

87
00:10:24,491 --> 00:10:25,981
你不会有事的
You'll be okay.

88
