No, l'll set the bone and take him for an x-ray later.

90
00:10:31,899 --> 00:10:33,127
好的 老爷
Very good, sir.

91
00:10:33,601 --> 00:10:37,298
- 对不起 老爷 - 别担心 他没事
-l'm very sorry, sir. l've told... -Don't worry. lt's fine.

92
