Just a little fall. lt's just a small fracture.

96
00:11:02,062 --> 00:11:03,859
你又想到那些蝙蝠?
The bats again?

97
00:11:07,033 --> 00:11:09,160
你知道他们为什么攻击你吗?
You know why they attacked you, don't you?

98
00:11:09,669 --> 00:11:12,729
- 因为他们怕你 - 他们怕我?
