100
00:11:15,041 --> 00:11:16,406
就连可怕的怪物也有?
Even the scary ones?

101
00:11:16,577 --> 00:11:18,442
尤其是可怕的怪物
Especially the scary ones.

102
00:11:18,812 --> 00:11:20,609
我给你看样东西
l got something to show you.

103
00:11:24,918 --> 00:11:28,217
- 你想你妈会喜欢吗? - 当然会
-You think your mother will like them? -Yeah.

104
00:11:28,889 --> 00:11:31,084
