-l think it's time to get up. -Maybe.

105
00:11:31,258 --> 00:11:32,850
不准赖床
No going back to bed.

106
00:11:36,096 --> 00:11:38,189
爸 高架铁路是你盖的吗?
Did you build this train, Dad?

107
00:11:38,365 --> 00:11:43,064
高谭市对韦恩家族很好 但这城市日渐没落
Gotham's been good to our family, but the city's been suffering.

108
00:11:43,237 --> 00:11:46,764
