People less fortunate than us have been enduring very hard times.

109
00:11:46,940 --> 00:11:50,876
于是我们建造经济的大众交通工具 把全体市民连结在一起
So we built a new, cheap, public transportation system to unite the city.

110
00:11:51,045 --> 00:11:52,740
正中央就是...
And at the center...

111
00:11:52,913 --> 00:11:54,744
韦恩大楼
...Wayne Tower.

112
00:11:54,915 --> 00:11:57,816
- 你在那里上班吗? - 不 我在医院工作
-ls that where you work? -No, l work at the hospital.

113
00:11:57,984 --> 00:12:01,181
我把公司交给更好的人管理
l leave the running of our company to much better men.

114
00:12:01,354 --> 00:12:03,219
- 比你更好的人? - 嗯...
-Better? -Well...

115
00:12:03,390 --> 00:12:05,654
比我对做生意更有兴趣的人
...more interested men.

116
00:13:02,049 --> 00:13:03,448
我们可以走吗?
Can we go?

117
00:13:05,819 --> 00:13:07,309
